{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_cello_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_cello_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"天空与流云","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"阿尔图罗在林间演奏，这是一首关于别离的旋律。她的演奏引来了一位意想不到的听众，她在演奏后见到了一位意想不到的客人。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_cello_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["阿米娅","？？？","特蕾西娅","阿尔图罗","“珂拉”","阿尔图罗？","伊万杰利斯塔十一世"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a0/Avg_bg_bg_outcounty.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":8},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cellodoubt","id":9},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":12,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":13},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":14},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":15},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":16},{"type":"charslot","id":17},{"type":"text","text":"风拨动深秋的乔木，琴声正随着落叶铺满整座树林。","id":18},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅随着琴声行进。她的右手微微攥起，戒指在林荫筛落的阳光里隐隐闪烁着光芒。","id":19},{"type":"dialog","id":20},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_501_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":21},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_972_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":22},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":23},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":24},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":25},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":26},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":28,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":29},{"type":"charslot","id":30},{"type":"text","text":"......黑发的萨科塔站在林间的空地上，拥抱着她的琴，那么专注。","id":31},{"type":"text","text":"琴声依然在“流动”，没有因自己的到来有任何停滞。琴声是温柔的。","id":32},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅停下了脚步，手掌慢慢放松下来。渐渐地，连身遭的树和远处的云都溶化成了水流，隐隐地在天际漾动，也在脚边漾动......","id":33},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"阿尔图罗小姐。","id":35,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"您不该随意离开您的房间，何况，今天有一场......","id":36,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":37},{"type":"charslot","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#2$1","duration":"1.5","id":39},{"type":"delay","time":"2.3","id":40},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","id":41},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":42},{"type":"text","text":"萨科塔女性轻轻抬动了眼眸，两人之间仍隔着不近的距离，但阿米娅确定对方看见了自己。","id":43},{"type":"dialog","id":44},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":45},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"charslot","id":47},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":48},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":49},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cellodoubt","id":50},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":51},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":52},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_bg_bg_wild_a.png","screenadapt":"showall","fadetime":"1.5","id":53},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_012_misa_1","duration":"1.5","id":54},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":55},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c7/Avg_bg_bg_cher_6.png","screenadapt":"showall","fadetime":"1.5","id":56},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#3","duration":"1.5","id":57},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":58},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/47/Avg_bg_bg_chercen_1.png","screenadapt":"showall","fadetime":"1.5","id":59},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_025_1","duration":"1.5","id":60},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":61},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f3/Avg_bg_21_G6_decisivebattlealley_n.png","screenadapt":"showall","fadetime":"1.5","id":62},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_245_1","duration":"1.5","id":63},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":64},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/63/Avg_bg_37_g3_fogblockadestreet_d.png","screenadapt":"showall","fadetime":"1.5","id":65},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":66},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":67},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2c/Avg_bg_34_g11_hispdwarshipdeck.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"1.5","id":68},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_868_1#7$1","duration":"1","id":69},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":70},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cellodoubth","id":71},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"showall","fadetime":"2.5","id":72},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","duration":"1.5","id":73},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":74},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅没有移动，但星光和浪涛主动拥抱了她，在万千迷离的景象里，无数熟悉的身影与她交错。","id":75},{"type":"text","text":"她觉得自己仿佛变成了一本书，而琴声像是一双手，向情感的最深处翻阅。","id":76},{"type":"text","text":"费德里科曾经警告过所有人，远离她的琴声。","id":77},{"type":"text","text":"但阿米娅不这么想。","id":78},{"type":"text","text":"她暗自深呼了一口气。","id":79},{"type":"text","text":"也只有她能这么做。能去碰触阿尔图罗神秘纱帐下的面目，能去碰触阿尔图罗自己。","id":80},{"type":"dialog","id":81},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":82},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":83},{"type":"charslot","id":84},{"type":"delay","time":"0.65","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"阿米娅，你在看什么？","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"唔？","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":88},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":89},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/eb/Avg_bg_27_g24_cloudy_sea.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":90},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":91},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":92},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅闻声回头，纯白如月光般的女性不知何时来到了自己的身后，目光温柔，一如往常。","id":93},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅从对方的眼眸中看见了自己的模样——","id":94},{"type":"text","text":"抱着膝盖坐在甲板的角落，刘海微微遮住眼睛。","id":95},{"type":"dialog","id":96},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_056","duration":"1","id":97},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_051","duration":"1","id":98},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":99},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_056","focus":"l","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"阿米娅，你已经在甲板上坐了好久了。你在看什么？","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_051","focus":"r","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"唔，太阳快要落下去了。","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"刚刚工程队的叔叔给了我一颗糖。特蕾西娅小姐，你们今天的工作结束了吗？","id":104,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_056","focus":"l","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"是的。你在想爸爸妈妈吗？","id":106,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_051","focus":"r","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"以前，爸爸结束工程队的工作回到家，都会抱着我到工棚的棚顶上去。","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"太阳落山的时候，气温会很快地降低。但爸爸的肩膀很厚，所以我们可以在上面待很长时间。","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"那个时候，星星也在一颗一颗地冒出来，很快就会挂满整个夜空......","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但现在，博士会陪着我，凯尔希医生会陪着我，您也会陪着我。","id":111,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我就......偶尔......不那么想爸爸妈妈了。","id":112,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_056","focus":"l","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"博士说，在你们游历这片大地的一年里，你才是那个给予对方以鼓舞的人。","id":115,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"很庆幸博士救下了你，我也很开心罗德岛能成为你的家。","id":116,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_051","focus":"r","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"嗯。","id":118,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_056","focus":"l","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"或许死亡并非最深刻的别离。但它一定是最残忍的，它无可挽回。","id":120,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"而你已经能勇敢地面对它。","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"或许未来，你还会经历更多别离。但记住，别离并不是终点。","id":122,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你将感受，你将连接，你将延续，你将作为一切的交汇。你将作为，未来。","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_051","focus":"r","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......嗯。","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_051.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_056","focus":"l","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"接下来你打算去哪里？","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_npc_056.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":128},{"type":"charslot","id":129},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_051","focus":"m","id":130},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":131},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#19$1","duration":"1.5","id":132},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"回去。","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-19$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#17$1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我......很感谢您。","id":136,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#21$1","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但我不会再停步不前了。","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ac/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-21$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":139},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":140},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":141},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":142},{"type":"text","text":"记忆中的特蕾西娅模糊了起来。","id":143},{"type":"text","text":"“魔王”会赠他人幻景，魔王传承记忆与技艺，传承情感与知识。","id":144},{"type":"text","text":"可阿米娅从来没有深究过自己。","id":145},{"type":"text","text":"就像两面镜子。阿米娅打开了那透明的门。","id":146},{"type":"dialog","id":147},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":148},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/94/Avg_bg_26_g5_laterano_chapelout.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":149},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":150},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":151},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":152},{"type":"text","text":"......而门外是一片草坪。","id":153},{"type":"text","text":"刚刚下过雨，空气的味道很好闻，不远处的小教堂沉默地矗立着——","id":154},{"type":"text","text":"所有的客人都已经离开，只剩下年幼的萨科塔站在一块墓碑前。","id":155},{"type":"text","text":"她沉默着，脸颊上还挂着水滴，分不清那是雨水还是眼泪。","id":156},{"type":"dialog","id":157},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#11$1","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......","id":159},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"所以，阿尔图罗小姐，这首旋律的主题，是“死亡”吗？","id":161,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你很悲伤，阿尔图罗小姐。你看，我也用了很久的时间，遇见了很多人，才能在想起爸爸妈妈的时候，不那么难过。","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"不止是悲伤，你还有疑惑和......愤怒？","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"针对什么？那些已经走掉的客人吗？还是，“死亡”本身？","id":164,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":165},{"type":"charslot","id":166},{"type":"text","text":"阿尔图罗并没有看见她。年幼的萨科塔伫立在曾经的岁月里。","id":167},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#9$1","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"妈妈，你用了多大的勇气，才勇敢地走出了那一步。","id":170},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#8$1","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"为什么死亡可以那么仓促地，掐断你的人生？","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"为什么死亡可以将人们的肉体变成一具空壳，那么简单就让所有复杂的、深刻的情感都消失不见？","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"为什么我们只能像一朵云？","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"那么自由，那么美好，但是风刮过就消失了。","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"它让我们为了弥补遗憾而做的所有努力，又变成了新的遗憾。","id":176},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":178},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#11$1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"而你本可以，不必死去。","id":180},{"type":"dialog","id":181},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":182},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":183},{"type":"charslot","id":184},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":185},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":186},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":187},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":188},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#10$1","duration":"1.5","id":189},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"珂拉，而你本可以，不必死去。","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"在女皇庆典开始之前，你有许多机会可以离开。","id":192},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“珂拉”","text":"阿尔图罗，在金盏花小巷的时候，在路德维格大学的时候，甚至在塔前剧场的时候，你也有许多机会告诉我你的心声。","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“珂拉”","text":"你不知该如何表达吗？可是你知道，我能听懂你的琴声。","id":195},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#8$1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我尝试过告诉薇薇安娜，希望她能通过金律乐章的线索，发现你的存在。","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"可即使是她......","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我不愿改变你的选择，我也无法改变你的选择。","id":199},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#10$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“珂拉”","text":"是啊。你其实比谁都清楚，我这一生，唯独在死去的时候，没有任何遗憾。","id":201},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#11$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“珂拉”","text":"遗憾的是你，不是吗？","id":203},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#10$1","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......","id":205},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#10$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“珂拉”","text":"我永远记得我们的相遇，在艾曼纽老师的葬礼上，在夕阳下的女皇双塔前......","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“珂拉”","text":"我帮你的琴调音，你向我讲述一路走来遇见的人、经历的事。","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“珂拉”","text":"我看不清你的面容，但我清楚地听见了你的琴声，很动人。","id":209},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#8$1","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"珂拉，你向我袒露你的遗憾，以及这些遗憾赋予你的信念。你是第一个主动邀请我演奏自己心声的人。","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......在漫长的漫游里，你是我为数不多的挚友。","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我不愿......","id":213},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#10$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“珂拉”","text":"可是，我的感情，我所经历过的一切，真的会像流云一般消散吗？","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“珂拉”","text":"阿尔图罗，我的挚友，为我演奏吧，让我再听一听你的琴声。","id":216},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#11$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“珂拉”","text":"我一直相信，这正是它所承载的意义。","id":218},{"type":"dialog","id":219},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cellodoubt","id":220},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":221},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":222},{"type":"charslot","id":223},{"type":"text","text":"琴声悠扬，更多未曾亲历的景象在阿尔图罗面前展开。那些画面、那些声音溶化成一条河流，流向人生的未可知处。","id":224},{"type":"text","text":"阿尔图罗在河流中跋涉。","id":225},{"type":"text","text":"不知道过了多久，也不知道是怎样上岸的，等她睁开眼睛的时候，已经站在了一扇门前。","id":226},{"type":"dialog","id":227},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":228},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_dooropen","id":229},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8e/Avg_bg_39_g7_chapel.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":230},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":231},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":232},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":233},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":234},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":235},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"走了很远吧？","id":237},{"type":"dialog","id":238},{"type":"charslot","id":239},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.7","duration":"1.5","id":240},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗？","text":"......","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗？","text":"这是一间修道院？","id":243},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"一间建设在移动地块上的修道院。和安布罗修修道院很像对吧？","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"它已经陪着我在大地上漫游了很多很多年。可现在，它已经停泊了两个半月了。","id":246},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.7","focus":"m","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗？","text":"它朽坏了吗？","id":248},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"不，只是我生病了而已。","id":250},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我正在等待，等待死亡如期而至。","id":252},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.7","focus":"m","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗？","text":"......","id":254},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"别看了，这里只有我一个人，也不会有其他人过来。","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"这里离拉特兰很远，远到那些为了“拉特兰主张”而奔走于整片大地的万国信使也未曾涉足。","id":257},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.7","focus":"m","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗？","text":"......","id":259},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我知道你想要问什么，阿尔图罗。","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"理想之所以为理想，在于它足够遥远。","id":262},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我去过许多地方，我靠近各个城市，进入散落着众多生命的荒野、冰原和沙漠......","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我去到每一处战火频仍的所在，我去到每一处被遗忘的止境......","id":265},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"漫长的漫游里，我从未放下我的琴。","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我为形形色色的人演奏，可结果依然不尽如人意。","id":268},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"强大的心灵、毫无保留的理解、纯粹而真挚的分享......我为靠近那个未来有过许多努力，但它还，很远。","id":270},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.7","focus":"m","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗？","text":"可是你将死在这里，一个僻远的角落，一间残破的修道院。死亡会将一切统统化作泡影，不会有任何事物留存下来。","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗？","text":"你正握着你的琴，你将演奏自己的死亡？以恐惧、无奈、愤怒和悲伤？","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗？","text":"就像曾经的你一样。","id":274},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......","id":276},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"窗外的云又聚起来了。","id":278},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.7","focus":"m","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗？","text":"什么？","id":280},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我们没法留住一朵云。可我们要描绘的，难道不是一整片天空吗？","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"伟人会死，凡人会死，同行者会离我们而去。没有人能够改写死亡。","id":283},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"它会掐断我们的人生，让我们的肉体变成一具空壳，它将不能承载任何思想、任何感受，不会再有新的内容从中产生。","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"可这并不意味着，我们曾有的那些复杂而深刻的情感，会就此消失。","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"正因为存在无法逾越的死亡，所以我必须演奏，不停地演奏。这样那些消失的情感，才能继续被所有人感受、理解与铭记。","id":287},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"这不正是它所承载的意义吗？","id":289},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.7","focus":"m","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗？","text":"阿尔图罗，你是否想过，刚才所见的，真的可能是自己的未来？","id":291},{"type":"dialog","id":292},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......","id":294},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我很高兴自己真的在靠近它。","id":296},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.7","focus":"m","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗？","text":"......","id":298},{"type":"dialog","id":299},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":300},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":302,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":303},{"type":"dialog","id":304},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":305},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":306},{"type":"charslot","id":307},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":308},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a0/Avg_bg_bg_outcounty.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":309},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_calm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":310,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":311},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":312},{"type":"text","text":"弦音仍在树林间回荡。萨科塔慢慢将大提琴放进琴箱，卡特斯女孩安静地看着对方的动作，等待她看向自己。","id":313},{"type":"dialog","id":314},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"阿米娅小姐？","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"很抱歉，把您卷进了我的旋律......","id":317},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"阿尔图罗小姐，您来罗德岛后，我们还没有机会正式打个招呼。","id":319,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"比起刻意的安排，今天这个场合，作为初见再合适不过了。","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您的能力很奇特。您甚至无需借助乐器......","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"就像......","id":323},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"两面镜子。","id":325,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"简简单单，却能看见无数个自己。","id":327},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您和罗德岛，都比我想象中的要有趣很多。","id":329},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#21$1","focus":"m","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"您的演奏也很有趣......仅仅是那么短的时间，我却觉得我们已经有了相当程度的了解。","id":331,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ac/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-21$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您也时常触碰那些情感吗？您会理解我的想法吗？","id":333},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#21$1","focus":"m","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"嗯。","id":335,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ac/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-21$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但我们终究是不同的，阿尔图罗小姐。","id":336,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ac/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-21$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"多可惜。","id":338},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"但我想我们还有很多时间共处。","id":340},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#21$1","focus":"m","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"那么，请您赶紧跟我回去吧。","id":342,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ac/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-21$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"不用这么焦急，我可并没有想要逃跑哦。","id":344},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但您确实擅离本舰有很长时间了。","id":346,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"而恰好，有一位来自拉特兰的贵客想要见您。","id":347,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我们可找您好久了呢......","id":348,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"原来如此，抱歉。","id":350},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"阿米娅小姐，回到船上后，不知是否还有机会正式邀请您参加我的演奏会？","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您可以不只成为一名听众。","id":353},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"没问题。我们欢迎所有对罗德岛怀有善意的人。","id":355,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"在您眼里，我怀有善意吗？","id":357},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"不，您的想法无关善恶，我已经清楚了。","id":359,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但我会确保这一点。","id":360,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":361},{"type":"charslot","id":362},{"type":"text","text":"没人再提起刚才发生的事情，一曲终了，演奏者与演奏者，听众与听众，总是有些默契。","id":363},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......我很喜欢这里的景色。但可惜，我不能再多待一会了。","id":365},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我们走吧。","id":367},{"type":"dialog","id":368},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":369},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":370},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":371},{"type":"charslot","id":372},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":373},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_bg_bg_room_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":374},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$tech_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_sys_tech_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":375,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":376},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":377},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":378},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":379},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":380},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......唔。","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"真是一位，“贵客”。","id":383},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"看来阿米娅小姐远比我想象的有能耐。","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"很荣幸见到您......教宗阁下。","id":386},{"type":"dialog","id":387},{"type":"charslot","id":388},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":389},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":390},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"对于刚才跑过去的几位感染者孩子而言，我只是“拉特兰的糖果爷爷”。","id":392,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"不是“教宗”。","id":393,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#2$1","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"悉听尊便。","id":395},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"阿尔图罗·吉亚洛。这应该是我们的第一次见面。","id":397,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"而你看起来并不惊讶。","id":398,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"看来莱塔尼亚之行，让你充分长了见识，宽阔了眼界。","id":399,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#4$1","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"和我有关，又需要罗德岛的负责人亲自安排的......我想确实该是一位大人物。","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"只是我以为，这样的场合会是在大教堂的大厅，教宗阁下会宣布对一位频频触犯禁忌的危险分子的判决。","id":402},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"唉，公证所登记在册的，与你相关的异常事件，数量确实有些多到不合适了。","id":404,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":405},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"等费德里科带你回到拉特兰，教皇厅将马上组织第一厅、第五厅、第六厅、第七厅，对相关案件进行联合审理。","id":406,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"当然，依据律法。","id":407,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"“律法”。","id":409},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"所以，在此之前，我们应该有一场会面。而它只能发生在罗德岛。","id":411,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#10$1","id":412},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......","id":413},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"阿尔图罗，罪孽之子。此刻，你可以将这间宿舍视作临时的告解室。","id":415,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"接下来我们谈及的所有内容，将不会被记录，在此后也不会被承认。","id":416,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我已有觉悟。","id":418},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"没有仪式，也无人见证。但也好，你本就不是什么英雄豪杰。","id":420,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我在此代表拉特兰，宣布你，阿尔图罗·吉亚洛......","id":422,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"受选为下一位“圣徒”。","id":423,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......","id":425},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"这似乎，并不是您的意志。","id":426},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#4$1","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"你这么觉得？","id":428,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":429},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"但其实这根本无关紧要。律法的选择一定有其意义。","id":430,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#4$1","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"是费德里科接应您来的罗德岛，对吧？","id":432},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我很好奇，在来的路上，您是如何向我们可爱的圣徒解释，他刚刚缉拿归案的逃犯，同样被选作了圣徒？","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"还是说......","id":434},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"费德里科确实还不知道这件事情。","id":436,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"但他会理解，我会要求他理解。","id":437,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"毕竟，我并不是真的在纵容或宽恕你的所作所为，孩子。","id":439,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","id":440},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我并不在乎律法的宽恕或是这个......名号。坦诚地说，还有点讨厌。","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"是教皇厅还有什么需要利用我的时候吗？","id":442},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"......孩子。","id":444,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"你并不了解所有事。你的经历，行为，理念，乃至反映到你法术之中的偏执......","id":445,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"都是出现过无数次的，萨科塔对萨科塔的一种解读。","id":446,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"你怎么确定，你的异禀天赋，你独一无二的法术......不是律法刻意的显现？","id":448,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"你终究头戴光环，是一个拉特兰的萨科塔，阿尔图罗。","id":449,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......","id":451},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"白色的石墙在拉特兰伫立千年万年，你也并不是唯一一个，“异类”，哦，我也不喜欢这个词。","id":453,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"但是，我们光辉的律法依然坚定地给了我答案。","id":454,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","id":455},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"阁下，请问这个模糊的“答案”，意味着什么？","id":456},{"type":"dialog","id":457},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":458},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":459},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":460},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"意味着......","id":461,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"......","id":462,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":463},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我们所知的任何光亮都有寂灭如黯的那一天。","id":464,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":465},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"它也不例外。","id":466,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":467},{"type":"charslot","id":468},{"type":"text","text":"老迈的教宗俏皮地指了指头顶的光环。","id":469},{"type":"text","text":"阿尔图罗陷入沉思。","id":470},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","id":471},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......即使萨科塔的一切都被解读成“它”赋予的？","id":472},{"type":"dialog","id":473},{"type":"charslot","id":474},{"type":"text","text":"教宗没有回答，反而唐突地询问了下一个问题。","id":475},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":476},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"你会是什么？","id":477,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","id":478},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我？什么？","id":479},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":480},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"除去你的偏执，你的傲慢，你的罪，你还会是什么？你还要做什么？还要带来什么？","id":481,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"你说呢？","id":482,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#10$1","id":483},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我在找，教宗阁下。","id":484},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"撒谎对您是无意义的。不过您说，光环会消失......萨科塔会失去信仰和温馨的小屋？","id":485},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"那不过是把拉特兰变得和其他地方一样而已。","id":486},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我所想的“理解”，我所想的“情感”，我所想的无所保留的，纯粹而坦诚的......“交流”。","id":487},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","id":488},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"与您说的事情没有关系。丁点没有。","id":489},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":490},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"......","id":491,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","id":492},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......即使如此，律法也坚持把我选做所谓的“圣徒”吗？","id":493},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":494},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"嗯......我会说，“是的”。","id":495,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":496},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"你给出了比我想象中更合理的答案，看来在莱塔尼亚发生的事情比情报文书里写的过分得多。","id":497,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","id":498},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......如果我拒绝成为圣徒呢？","id":499},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"还是说，这是您为我安排的“赎罪”，我并没有选择的权利？","id":500},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":501},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"孩子。选择权依然在你。","id":502,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我只是向一位拉特兰公民，传达我所收到的警示而已。","id":503,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","id":504},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"站在圣迹最顶点的您，将选择权交给一个罪人？","id":505},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":506},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"只是你也知道，教宗总是会巧妙地撬动神谕里的字句，比如，在圣徒的人选上换一个名字之类的。","id":507,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#10$1","id":508},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......","id":509},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":510},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"别误会。我没有在威胁你。反正费德里科会处理好的。","id":511,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#7$1","id":512},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您既然依然这么想，又为什么——","id":513},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":514},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"——但在太阳落下的时候，你的所思所想也许会是一剂良药。","id":515,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"“圣徒”是萨科塔岌岌可危的一个讯号。我只能，更不择手段一点。","id":516,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":517},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"再者，你引发的悲剧也是你自身的悲剧。","id":518,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"萨科塔，拉特兰，信仰，共感，交流，我们的社会。这些东西构成了你的故事，构成了你。","id":519,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"那哪一位教宗不该对此负责？","id":520,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":521},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"所以，在深刻反思后，我决定亲自领你走向终点，小圣徒。在你的使命完成之后。","id":522,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":523},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"领你们每一个人，得到你们应得的未来。","id":524,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","id":525},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"什么样的终点？","id":526},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":527},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我不知道。我可不是什么大先知。","id":528,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"......当然，就现状来看，你应得的未来可谈不上前途光明。","id":529,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","id":530},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"看得出，您做出这样的决定，也承担了不少压力。","id":531},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":532},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"情况也许真的糟糕到了我们要赌一把的地步。","id":533,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"如何，阿尔图罗？","id":534,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","id":535},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"那么......","id":536},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您能否接受，成为一位圣徒的听众？","id":537},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":538},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我对音乐懂的不多，不过先等等......","id":539,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"站太久了，我们就不能去罗德岛舒适的会客室坐一会吗？","id":540,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","id":541},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您可以边走边听。","id":542},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":543},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"好，好。嘿哟。","id":544,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":545},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"请开始吧。我想听些更“拉特兰”一点的调子。","id":546,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":547},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":548},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":549},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":550},{"type":"text","text":"窗外，白日的尾巴倔强地在天空留下轮廓，暮色灿烂。","id":551},{"type":"text","text":"她没来由地想起崔林特尔梅的晚霞，想起曾见过的许多个城市的云。","id":552},{"type":"text","text":"天色已经渐渐暗了，而脚下传来轻微的晃动，这艘船即将驶入黑夜。","id":553},{"type":"text","text":"舰桥上的灯亮了。","id":554},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","id":555},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"那......","id":556},{"type":"dialog","id":557},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#2$1","id":558},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":559},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cellodoubt","id":560},{"type":"text","text":"旋律响起。","id":561},{"type":"dialog","id":562},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":563},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":564},{"type":"dialog","id":565},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":566},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":567},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":568},{"type":"charslot","id":569},{"type":"image","id":570}],"characters":["阿米娅","？？？","特蕾西娅","阿尔图罗","“珂拉”","阿尔图罗？","伊万杰利斯塔十一世"]}